{
  "video_id": "_B9A3J70IPQ",
  "title": "The forgotten art of the zoetrope | Eric Dyer",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12890.0,
      "end_time": 14567.0,
      "text": "A long time ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14591.0,
      "end_time": 16338.0,
      "text": "I was a professional animator."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18393.0,
      "end_time": 19543.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19567.0,
      "end_time": 21473.0,
      "text": "[Eric Dyer]"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21497.0,
      "end_time": 22507.0,
      "text": "[Animator]"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22531.0,
      "end_time": 23680.0,
      "text": "[Compositor]"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28245.0,
      "end_time": 29971.0,
      "text": "And at night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29995.0,
      "end_time": 32278.0,
      "text": "I would make my own experimental films."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32302.0,
      "end_time": 33355.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 33379.0,
      "end_time": 38100.0,
      "text": "And I was spending a lot of time, way too much time, in front of a screen"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38340.0,
      "end_time": 40729.0,
      "text": "for work that would be presented on a screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40753.0,
      "end_time": 44476.0,
      "text": "and I had this great need to get my hands back on the work again."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46640.0,
      "end_time": 48281.0,
      "text": "Now, before \"The Simpsons,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48305.0,
      "end_time": 49461.0,
      "text": "before \"Gumby,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49485.0,
      "end_time": 51163.0,
      "text": "before \"Betty Boop,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51187.0,
      "end_time": 54643.0,
      "text": "before there was such a thing as cinema and television,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54667.0,
      "end_time": 57591.0,
      "text": "animation was hugely popular in this form."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57615.0,
      "end_time": 59246.0,
      "text": "This is a zoetrope."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59270.0,
      "end_time": 61510.0,
      "text": "And you spin this drum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61750.0,
      "end_time": 63944.0,
      "text": "and you look through the slits into the inside of the drum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63968.0,
      "end_time": 66930.0,
      "text": "and you see the animation pop to life."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66612.0,
      "end_time": 69309.0,
      "text": "This is animation in physical form,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 69334.0,
      "end_time": 72617.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s animation I could get my hands on again."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 73260.0,
      "end_time": 75110.0,
      "text": "I took these ideas to Denmark."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 75134.0,
      "end_time": 77988.0,
      "text": "I went there with my family on a Fulbright Fellowship."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 78850.0,
      "end_time": 80175.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s my daughter, Mia."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82736.0,
      "end_time": 85232.0,
      "text": "I rode around the city on my bicycle"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 85256.0,
      "end_time": 88595.0,
      "text": "and shot all the interesting moving elements of Copenhagen:"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 91120.0,
      "end_time": 92708.0,
      "text": "the boaters in the canals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 93875.0,
      "end_time": 95940.0,
      "text": "the colors that explode in spring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 96501.0,
      "end_time": 98164.0,
      "text": "the free-use city bikes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 98691.0,
      "end_time": 99880.0,
      "text": "love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 100472.0,
      "end_time": 101676.0,
      "text": "textures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 102148.0,
      "end_time": 103494.0,
      "text": "the healthy cuisine --"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 103519.0,
      "end_time": 104669.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 106395.0,
      "end_time": 109701.0,
      "text": "And I brought all that video back into the physical world"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 109725.0,
      "end_time": 112414.0,
      "text": "by printing it out on these long strips of ink-jet paper"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 112439.0,
      "end_time": 113747.0,
      "text": "and cutting out the forms."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 114154.0,
      "end_time": 117488.0,
      "text": "Now, I invented my own form of the zoetrope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 118600.0,
      "end_time": 121689.0,
      "text": "which removes the drum"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121713.0,
      "end_time": 126508.0,
      "text": "and replaces the slits with a video camera."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 127916.0,
      "end_time": 130586.0,
      "text": "And this was very exciting for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 130610.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134795.0,
      "text": "because it meant that I could make these physical objects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 134819.0,
      "end_time": 137166.0,
      "text": "and I could make films from those objects."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 138153.0,
      "end_time": 140167.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s me riding on my bicycle."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 140191.0,
      "end_time": 141341.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 146942.0,
      "end_time": 150995.0,
      "text": "I made about 25 paper sculptures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 151190.0,
      "end_time": 153160.0,
      "text": "each the size of a bicycle wheel."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 154110.0,
      "end_time": 156517.0,
      "text": "I brought them into the studio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 156541.0,
      "end_time": 157731.0,
      "text": "spun them"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 157755.0,
      "end_time": 160999.0,
      "text": "and shot them to make the film \"Copenhagen Cycles.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 161230.0,
      "end_time": 163884.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 169873.0,
      "end_time": 173534.0,
      "text": "This project not only allowed me to get my hands back on the work again"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 173558.0,
      "end_time": 175459.0,
      "text": "but it helped me get my life back."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 176160.0,
      "end_time": 181429.0,
      "text": "Instead of spending 12, 15 hours a day with my face plastered to a screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 181453.0,
      "end_time": 185120.0,
      "text": "I was having these little adventures with our new family"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 185360.0,
      "end_time": 187796.0,
      "text": "and shooting video along the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 187820.0,
      "end_time": 190941.0,
      "text": "and it was kind of a symbiosis of art and life."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 191550.0,
      "end_time": 193548.0,
      "text": "And I think that it&#39;s no mistake"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 193572.0,
      "end_time": 197398.0,
      "text": "that zoetrope translates into \"wheel of life.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 197422.0,
      "end_time": 201422.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 203700.0,
      "end_time": 205494.0,
      "text": "But film and video does flatten sculpture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 205518.0,
      "end_time": 207546.0,
      "text": "so I tried to imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 207570.0,
      "end_time": 211498.0,
      "text": "a way that animated sculpture could be experienced as such,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 211522.0,
      "end_time": 215569.0,
      "text": "and also a completely immersive kind of animated sculpture."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 215593.0,
      "end_time": 219262.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s where I came up with the idea for the zoetrope tunnel."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 219635.0,
      "end_time": 221743.0,
      "text": "You walk through with a handheld strobe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 221767.0,
      "end_time": 223859.0,
      "text": "and wherever you point the flashlight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 223883.0,
      "end_time": 225360.0,
      "text": "the animation pops to life."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 226450.0,
      "end_time": 229523.0,
      "text": "I plan to finish this project in the next 30 to 40 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 229547.0,
      "end_time": 230697.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 232240.0,
      "end_time": 234933.0,
      "text": "But I did build a half-scale prototype."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 236441.0,
      "end_time": 237983.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s covered in Velcro,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 238700.0,
      "end_time": 241523.0,
      "text": "and I could lay inside on this bridge"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 241547.0,
      "end_time": 244869.0,
      "text": "and stick animated sequences to the walls"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 244893.0,
      "end_time": 246133.0,
      "text": "and test stuff out."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 247790.0,
      "end_time": 251238.0,
      "text": "People would comment that it reminded them of an MRI."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 253260.0,
      "end_time": 256178.0,
      "text": "And that medical connection spoke to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 256202.0,
      "end_time": 257723.0,
      "text": "because at the age of 14,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 257747.0,
      "end_time": 260320.0,
      "text": "I was diagnosed with a degenerative retinal condition"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 260344.0,
      "end_time": 262826.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s slowly taking my vision away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 262850.0,
      "end_time": 265315.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;d never responded to that in my work."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 265954.0,
      "end_time": 269610.0,
      "text": "So I responded to it in this piece called, \"Implant.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 270841.0,
      "end_time": 274733.0,
      "text": "It is an imaginary, super-magnified medical device"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 274757.0,
      "end_time": 276760.0,
      "text": "that fits around the optic nerve."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 278648.0,
      "end_time": 282451.0,
      "text": "And the public is, in a sense, miniaturized to experience it."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 288270.0,
      "end_time": 289770.0,
      "text": "With a handheld strobe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 289795.0,
      "end_time": 292853.0,
      "text": "they can explore the sculpture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 292877.0,
      "end_time": 297843.0,
      "text": "and discover thousands of cell-sized robots"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 297867.0,
      "end_time": 301147.0,
      "text": "hard at work, leaping in and out of the optic nerve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 301171.0,
      "end_time": 302570.0,
      "text": "being deployed to the retina"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 302595.0,
      "end_time": 303745.0,
      "text": "to repair it."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 304810.0,
      "end_time": 308572.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s my science fiction fantasy cure of my own incurable disorder."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 308596.0,
      "end_time": 310538.0,
      "text": "(Machine buzzes)"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 311109.0,
      "end_time": 315505.0,
      "text": "Now, in the real-world gene therapy and gene therapy research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 315529.0,
      "end_time": 320130.0,
      "text": "healthy genes are being administered to unhealthy cells using viruses."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 321110.0,
      "end_time": 324822.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a lot of colorful, fluffy hope in this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 324846.0,
      "end_time": 328225.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s also some creepy, threatening idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 328249.0,
      "end_time": 332355.0,
      "text": "of viruses maybe becoming an invasive species in your body."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 335881.0,
      "end_time": 339875.0,
      "text": "Vision loss has helped to take me away from the things"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 339899.0,
      "end_time": 342162.0,
      "text": "that disconnect me from the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 343520.0,
      "end_time": 345358.0,
      "text": "Instead of being sealed off in an automobile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 345382.0,
      "end_time": 347550.0,
      "text": "I ride my bike,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 347790.0,
      "end_time": 348717.0,
      "text": "take buses and trains"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 348741.0,
      "end_time": 350139.0,
      "text": "and walk a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 350579.0,
      "end_time": 355559.0,
      "text": "And instead of a visually intensive process in the studio, primarily,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 355583.0,
      "end_time": 358169.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m also getting outdoors a lot more"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 358193.0,
      "end_time": 359941.0,
      "text": "and using more of my senses."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 360916.0,
      "end_time": 365599.0,
      "text": "This landscape is a couple hours east of San Diego, California."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 365623.0,
      "end_time": 367268.0,
      "text": "My brother lives out that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 368608.0,
      "end_time": 371313.0,
      "text": "He and I went camping there for four days."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 372402.0,
      "end_time": 374485.0,
      "text": "And I grabbed my camera,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 374509.0,
      "end_time": 376435.0,
      "text": "and I walked through the canyons."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 376459.0,
      "end_time": 379505.0,
      "text": "And I tried to imagine and figure out"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 379529.0,
      "end_time": 382627.0,
      "text": "what kind of motion would be present"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 382651.0,
      "end_time": 387205.0,
      "text": "in this place that was so still and so devoid of motion."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 387229.0,
      "end_time": 389478.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s the stillest place I&#39;ve ever been."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 390153.0,
      "end_time": 395330.0,
      "text": "And I realized that it was the movement of my own body through the landscape"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 395354.0,
      "end_time": 397150.0,
      "text": "that was creating the animation."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 397426.0,
      "end_time": 399651.0,
      "text": "It was the motion of changing perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 400129.0,
      "end_time": 403613.0,
      "text": "So I created this piece called \"Mud Caves\" from those photographs."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 404162.0,
      "end_time": 406637.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a multilayered print piece,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 406661.0,
      "end_time": 409304.0,
      "text": "and you can think of it as a zoetrope laid flat."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 410200.0,
      "end_time": 413361.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s kind of my western landscape panorama."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 413849.0,
      "end_time": 416989.0,
      "text": "And next to the print piece there&#39;s a video monitor"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 417130.0,
      "end_time": 420491.0,
      "text": "that shows the animation hidden within the artwork."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 421600.0,
      "end_time": 423818.0,
      "text": "I think one of the best parts about this project for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 423843.0,
      "end_time": 426502.0,
      "text": "was that I got to hang out with my brother a lot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 426526.0,
      "end_time": 429670.0,
      "text": "who lives 2,500 miles away from me."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 429799.0,
      "end_time": 434257.0,
      "text": "And we would just sit in this seemingly eternal landscape"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 434281.0,
      "end_time": 437570.0,
      "text": "sculpted by water over millions of years"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 437810.0,
      "end_time": 438231.0,
      "text": "and talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 438747.0,
      "end_time": 440922.0,
      "text": "We&#39;d talk about our kids growing up"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 440946.0,
      "end_time": 443507.0,
      "text": "and the slowing pace of our parents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 443531.0,
      "end_time": 448648.0,
      "text": "and our dad who&#39;s suffering from leukemia, memory loss and infection."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 449475.0,
      "end_time": 452293.0,
      "text": "And it struck me that, as individuals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 452317.0,
      "end_time": 453890.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re finite,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 453914.0,
      "end_time": 455366.0,
      "text": "but as a family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 455390.0,
      "end_time": 457508.0,
      "text": "we are an ongoing cycle --"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 457532.0,
      "end_time": 459399.0,
      "text": "a kind of wheel of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 460716.0,
      "end_time": 464639.0,
      "text": "Now, I want to leave you with a tribute to one of my mentors."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 465236.0,
      "end_time": 470815.0,
      "text": "She reminds me that physical presence is important"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 470839.0,
      "end_time": 474193.0,
      "text": "and that play is not a luxury,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 474217.0,
      "end_time": 475501.0,
      "text": "but a necessity."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 482566.0,
      "end_time": 483772.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s Pixie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 484555.0,
      "end_time": 486953.0,
      "text": "and she&#39;s our family dog."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 490796.0,
      "end_time": 492566.0,
      "text": "And she loves to jump."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 492590.0,
      "end_time": 493969.0,
      "text": "(Dog barking)"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 493994.0,
      "end_time": 496457.0,
      "text": "(Dog barking and spring boinging)"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 500466.0,
      "end_time": 503101.0,
      "text": "And this is a new kind of zoetrope"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 503125.0,
      "end_time": 505404.0,
      "text": "that I developed at the Imaging Research Center"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 505428.0,
      "end_time": 506948.0,
      "text": "at UMBC in Baltimore."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 508925.0,
      "end_time": 511148.0,
      "text": "And I call it a \"real-time zoetrope.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 511172.0,
      "end_time": 513755.0,
      "text": "(Dog barking)"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 513779.0,
      "end_time": 516145.0,
      "text": "(Dog barking and spring boinging)"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 517549.0,
      "end_time": 518700.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 518725.0,
      "end_time": 519878.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}